lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e1bf39e65f352f0f3a8644e063766921ec738a","tid":441954,"uid":14867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你可以質疑佢某幾首新歌難聽到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你唔可以否認佢把聲係歌壇入面有極穩定發揮<br />\n有人話佢係歌歌機器，冇感情<br />\n不過我自己覺得佢唱得好有意境（當然大部分講緊舊歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">飛花</span>、一生不變、天河、<span style=\"color: red;\">花落誰家⋯</span><br />\n就算係新返少少 戀愛為何物、一個都不能少⋯都好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過見佢呢個歲數仲出嚟開show搵銀都覺得有啲灰<br />\n同佢同期果堆好多都hea下hea下過人世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅字個兩首真心正，其實我唔明點解啲人話佢無乜感情，明明佢個種係淡淡散發出嚟嘅感情。"},{"pid":"6291671bfbe1c1f25d9696e3cb2a0d4bdea65c1c","tid":441954,"uid":102826,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"對李克勤真係冇咩好感，唱腔永遠一鳩樣，份人又鳩下鳩下成日柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071fc0eaacadc407bd4aa24020325615a64e6ae8","tid":441954,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"今年唔係側田+衛蘭男女金咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f74af49ab2dad554ff4794378335fe4fa1f2de","tid":441954,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懷疑樓豬係其他唱片公司打手<br />\n你隻碟有質素<br />\n就算譚伯拎我都服<br />\n唔應該睇年紀睇輩份<br />\n<br />\n而且克勤唔好聽咩<br />\nC3po幾正<br />\n加上其他男歌手冇乜紅歌<br />\n最紅已經係長相廝守</blockquote><br />\nc3po真係好聽，不過其他麻麻"},{"pid":"14e773e1393903996665ce0f3b8bcfbabf47f4a8","tid":441954,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20